      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Fabio Gobbato</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:189px;\"><a href=\"https://www.g-sei.org/i-g-t-2013//\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/9/9d/FabioGobbato.jpg\" width=\"187\" height=\"230\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:FabioGobbato.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Fabio Gobbato <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Fabio Gobbato</b>,<br />\nan Italian computer chess programmer, and author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant chess engine <a href=\"/Pedone\" title=\"Pedone\">Pedone</a>, which had it tournament debut at the <a href=\"/IGT_2013\" title=\"IGT 2013\">IGT 2013</a>, and already won the <a href=\"/IGT_2014\" title=\"IGT 2014\">IGT 2014</a> with 6/7! \nHe has further written the didactic open source chess engine <a href=\"/QBBEngine\" title=\"QBBEngine\">QBBEngine</a> to demonstrate how to use <a href=\"/Quad-Bitboards\" title=\"Quad-Bitboards\">quad-bitboards</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>,\nand the tool <i>ParserCutechess</i>, which parses the output of <a href=\"/Cutechess-cli\" title=\"Cutechess-cli\">Cutechess-cli</a> to create <a href=\"/Match_Statistics\" title=\"Match Statistics\">match statistics</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. In July 2021, Fabio Gobbato announced his chess engine <a href=\"/Revenge\" title=\"Revenge\">Revenge</a> as commercial  successor of Pedone <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2014\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2014</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2016_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2016 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fabio_Gobbato&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2014\">2014</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fabio_Gobbato&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2014\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53289\">Killer and move encoding</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 14, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Encoding_Moves\" title=\"Encoding Moves\">Encoding Moves</a>, <a href=\"/Killer_Heuristic\" title=\"Killer Heuristic\">Killer Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53657\">Tune cut margins with Texel/gaviota tuning method</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 11, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53972\">Your experience with PVS + Aspiration window</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 07, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/PVS_and_Aspiration\" title=\"PVS and Aspiration\">PVS and Aspiration</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54021\">A little improvement to the Texel's tuning method</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 11, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54640\">Pedone 1.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 14, 2014 </li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015\">2015</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fabio_Gobbato&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55265\">Optimization algorithm for the Texel/Gaviota tuning method</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 09, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55563\">Parallel iterative search function</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 05, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a>, <a href=\"/Iterative_Search\" title=\"Iterative Search\">Iterative Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=56931\">Fixed nodes self tuning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 09, 2015 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=57067\">Asymmetric evaluation function</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 24, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Asymmetric_Evaluation\" title=\"Asymmetric Evaluation\">Asymmetric Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=57650\">Games adjudication</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 15, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=57969\">ELO error margin</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 17, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Match_Statistics\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Match Statistics</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=58556\">xboard and fifty move rule</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 11, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/XBoard\" title=\"XBoard\">XBoard</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=58647&amp;start=11\">Re: Unifying make/undo and copy-make</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 22, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Copy-Make\" title=\"Copy-Make\">Copy-Make</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2016_...\">2016 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fabio_Gobbato&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2016 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=59801\">Profile multithreaded engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 09, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Profiling&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Profiling (page does not exist)\">Profiling</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=60195\">Nalimov egtb probing code</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 16, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Nalimov_Tablebases\" title=\"Nalimov Tablebases\">Nalimov Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=61875\">Evaluation doubt</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 29, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=62239&amp;start=2\">Hashing a quadboard from scratch</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 24, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Hash_Table\" title=\"Hash Table\">Hash Table</a>, <a href=\"/Quad-Bitboards\" title=\"Quad-Bitboards\">Quad-Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=70139\">New release Pedone 1.9</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 08, 2019</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fabio_Gobbato&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=74777\">Neural Networks weights type</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 13, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">Neural Networks</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish_NNUE\" title=\"Stockfish NNUE\">Stockfish NNUE</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=74955\">Train a neural network evaluation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 01, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a>, <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75042\">Neural network quantization</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 08, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">Neural Networks</a>, <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=77684\">New commercial engine Revenge 1.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 09, 2021</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fabio_Gobbato&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.revengechess.com/\">Revenge chess engine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/pedonechess/\">Pedone</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/pedonechess/a-didactic-engine\">QBBEngine - A didactic engine</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fabio_Gobbato&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.g-sei.org/i-g-t-2013//\">International Gsei Tournament 2013 «&#160;G 6</a>, Fabio Gobbato at <a href=\"/IGT_2013\" title=\"IGT 2013\">IGT 2013</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/pedonechess/a-didactic-engine\">QBBEngine - A didactic engine</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=63888&amp;start=2\">Re: MATCH sanity</a> by <a href=\"/Salvatore_Giannotti\" title=\"Salvatore Giannotti\">Salvatore Giannotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 03, 2017</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=77684\">New commercial engine Revenge 1.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Fabio Gobbato</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 09, 2021</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228140324\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.019 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 87/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 178/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6261-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228140324 and revision id 25543\n -->\n"
